'''蛋白激酶C'''（{{lang-en|Protein kinase C}}，简称'''PKC'''，EC编号：2.7.11.13）是一種[[蛋白质|蛋白质]][[激酶|激酶]]家族，通过将其它[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]的[[丝氨酸|丝氨酸]]/[[苏氨酸|苏氨酸]]侧链上的[[羟基|羟基]][[磷酸化|磷酸化]]来调节这些蛋白的活性。而蛋白激酶C也受[[二酸甘油酯|二酸甘油酯]]（DAG）或[[钙|钙]]离子(Ca<sup>2+</sup>)浓度的调控<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Wilson CH, Ali ES, Scrimgeour N, Martin AM, Hua J, Tallis GA, Rychkov GY, Barritt GJ |title=Steatosis inhibits liver cell store-operated Ca²⁺ entry and reduces ER Ca²⁺ through a protein kinase C-dependent mechanism |journal=The Biochemical Journal |volume=466 |issue=2 |pages=379–90 |year=2015 |pmid=25422863 |doi=10.1042/BJ20140881 }}</ref>，因此蛋白激酶C在几个[[信号通路|信号通路]]中扮演重要角色。

在人类基因组中，15个[[同工酶|同工酶]]构成了PKC家族<ref name="pmid9601053">{{cite journal | vauthors = Mellor H, Parker PJ | title = The extended protein kinase C superfamily | journal = The Biochemical Journal | volume = 332 | issue = Pt 2 | pages = 281–92 | date = Jun 1998 | pmid = 9601053 | pmc = 1219479 | doi = 10.1042/bj3320281 | url = http://www.biochemj.org/bj/332/bj3320281.htm | series = 332 | access-date = 2013-11-20 | archive-date = 2002-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20021022115912/http://www.biochemj.org/bj/332/bj3320281.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。这些同工酶可依所需[[第二信使|第二信使]]的不同分为三类：典型或传统的PKC（classical or conventional PKC,cPKC）；新型的PKC（novel PKC,nPKC）；非典型的PKC（atypicalPKC,aPKC）<ref name="pmid7737456">{{cite journal | vauthors = Nishizuka Y | title = Protein kinase C and lipid signaling for sustained cellular responses | journal = FASEB Journal | volume = 9 | issue = 7 | pages = 484–96 | date = Apr 1995 | pmid = 7737456 | doi =  | url = http://www.fasebj.org/cgi/content/abstract/9/7/484 | format = abstract | access-date = 2016-02-22 | archive-date = 2009-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091225082758/http://www.fasebj.org/cgi/content/abstract/9/7/484 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。传统的PKC包括{{tsl|en|isoforms|蛋白質異形體|異形體}}α、β<sub>I</sub>、β<sub>II</sub>和γ，需要Ca<sup>2+</sup>、[[二酸甘油酯|二酸甘油酯]]和[[磷脂|磷脂]]类物质（如[[磷脂絲胺酸|磷脂絲胺酸]]）来激活。新型的PKC包括δ、ε、η和θ同工酶，需要DAG来激活，但不需要Ca<sup>2+</sup>。因此，传统和新型的PKC都参与[[磷脂酶C|磷脂酶C]]的[[信号转导|信号转导]]通路。而非典型的PKC，包括ζ和ι / λ，既不需要Ca<sup>2+</sup>，也不需要DAG激活。

